ald Partners[62] John Stagliano, founder and owner of Evil Angel[66] Jeff Yass, managing director and co-founder of Susquehanna International Group[67] Media personalities[edit] Drew Carey Actors and comedians[edit] Penn Jillete Diedrich Bader, actor[68] Drew Carey, comedian[69] Brando Eaton, actor[70] Penn Jillette, of Penn & Teller[71] Melissa Joan Hart, actress[72] Larry the Cable Guy, comedian[73] Raven-Symoné, actress, singer, television personality[74] Joe Rogan, comedian, actor[75] Doug Stanhope, comedian, actor, 2008 presidential candidate [76] Teller, of Penn & Teller[77] Brendon Walsh, comedian[20] Randy Wayne, actor[78] Kurt Yaeger, actor[79] Elliott Morgan, YouTube personality and former SourceFed host[80] Directors and screenwriters[edit] Heywood Gould, director and screenwriter[81] David Lynch, director and screenwriter[82] Athletes and sports figures[edit] Kevin Nash Rudy Carpenter, football quarterback[51] Hal Gill, retired professional ice hockey player[51] Goldust, professional wrestler[83] Kane, professional wrestler[84] John Layfield, professional wrestler[84] Chris Long, NFL football player[85] Kevin Nash, professional wrestler[86] Aron Price, professional golfer[87] Kenny Smith, broadcaster and former NBA basketball player.[88] Val Venis, professional wrestler[89] Sean Waltman, professional wrestler[90] Musicians and artists[edit] Krist Novoselić Krist Novoselić, musician, bassist and co-founder of Nirvana[91] Kurt Rock, rapper, activist, singer, music producer and CEO of KWP Music Group[92] Commentators, writers, and columnists[edit] Peter Bagge, cartoonist and Reason contributor[93] Ronald Bailey, science writer[94] Joshua Brown, author of The Reformed Broker blog and commentator on CNBC[95] Jay Cost, writer for The Weekly Standard[96] Kmele Foster, co-host of The Independents, political pundit[97] Nick Gillespie, editor of Reason.com and Reason.tv[98] Jack Hunter, Politics editor for Rare.us[99] Jeff Jacoby, columnist for The Boston Globe[10